#Brainwave_Matrix_Intern #Task_2
# 🛒 E-Commerce Website

This is a responsive and interactive **E-Commerce Website** built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. It simulates a simple online shopping experience where users can browse products, add items to the cart, and proceed to checkout.

---

## 📌 Features

- 🌐 Responsive user interface
- 🛍️ Product listing with images, names, and prices
- ➕ Add to Cart functionality
- 🧮 Dynamic cart with item count and total price calculation
- ❌ Remove items from cart
- 💳 Checkout interface (mock)
- 🧭 Smooth navigation and interactive layout

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **HTML5** – Structure of the website  
- **CSS3** – Styling and layout  
- **JavaScript** – Dynamic content and interactivity  

---

## 📁 Folder Structure
ecommerce-website/
│
├── index.html # Main HTML file
├── style.css # Styling (CSS)
├── script.js # Functionality (JavaScript)
└── images/ # Product images

---

## 📚 Future Improvements

- 🧾 Checkout form
- 🔐 User login/authentication
- 🗃️ Backend integration with database (Node.js or Firebase)
- 🛒 Persistent cart using local storage

